text: Amjad Walid Hussein (, born 9 November 1993) is an Iraqi footballer who plays as a winger for Al-Shorta in the Iraqi Premier League.Amjad Waleed Hussein at WorldFootball.com ==International career== On August 26, 2015, Walid made his first international cap with Iraq against Lebanon in a friendly match. ==Honours== ===Club=== ;Duhok * Iraqi Premier League: 2009–10 ;Al-Shorta * Iraqi Premier League: 2018–19 ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:Sportspeople from Baghdad Category:Al-Shorta SC players
